famous director xie pingan retained the distinguishing feature of peking opera in the overall presentation and at the same time added the romantic , vivid and emotional appeal of a fairy tale . xie mobilized a large amount of artistic means and stage glossary , especially in the handling of scenes with many actors , and allow the audience to feel his exceptional skills and unique style .
china &apos;s grade one actor and winner of the &quot; plum blossom award &quot; , zhang yimling , plays the role of eliza .
her voice is sweet , loud and clear .
amid the beautiful sentiment in a foreign country , eliza felt sorrow about her beloved brother and sang a long passage of counter &quot; erhuang &quot; . the singing was so rich in sentiment and her voice was so lovely . everything was so merry and lively and no words can properly describe it .
the stage appearance was close to life ; the simple but pretty hair ornaments all provided exceptional luster to her .
car bomb killed 4 four people in columbia
xinhua news agency , bogota , january 16 ( reporter : yin nan ) - a car bomb exploded near the local prosecution office in the city center of medellin , columbia &apos;s second largest city , in the morning of the 16th . the blast killed 4 people and injured 26 others .
the columbian police said a rental car parked in the car park of a shopping mall next to the prosecution office exploded at 8 : 05 a.m.
the death toll included a one-year old child and five of the injured were in critical conditions .
the blast damaged 40 shops and 15 cars in the vicinity .
as 68 members of the revolutionary armed forces of colombia were captured in medellin this week , authority suspects the crime might have been committed by this anti-government guerilla organization .
medellin police chief leonardo gallego announced a police reward of 500 million pesos ( about us $ 172 thousand ) for the capture of the troublemaker .
medellin is situated in the antioquia state , which is one of the areas with most serious armed conflicts in columbia . illegal armed forces , including the revolutionary armed forces of columbia , national liberation army and right-wing paramilitaries etc . , are all active in this region .
european union identified a huge diamond deal as a monopoly
xinhua news agency , brussels , january 16 ( reporter : tian fan ) - the european committee announced on the 16th that european union ( eu ) has preliminary identified the 4 billion euro diamond contract between de beers group , the largest diamond supplier in the world , and the russian diamond company as a violation of eu anti-monopoly law .
de beers , which has headquarters in both south africa and britain , controls 60-65 % of the world &apos;s uncut diamond market . the russian diamond company is the only diamond mining company in russia and is the second biggest uncut diamond producer in the world .
according to the terms of the huge sum five-year contract between the two companies , the russian diamond company agreed to sell half of its annual diamond production to de beers and that is , uncut diamonds with a value of 800 million euros . de beers will be responsible to market these diamonds in the market .
the european committee pointed out in a statement that the contract would restrict the free competition in russia and the world diamond market . de beers might abuse its leading position and effectively controls the quantities , quality and price of diamonds in the world market .
according to anti-monopoly law in eu , the two companies may object to the european committee &apos;s decision within two months . the european committee will also continue its anti-monopoly investigation on these two companies .
a gas explosion took place at jixi &apos;s lishu mine
xinhua news agency , harbin , january 21 ( reporter : wu xiaodong and yang haibin ) - a gas explosion took place at 9 : 42 on the 20th at jixi mine group &apos;s lishu coal mine no. 7 , when 97 people were working in the pits . the blast killed 16 people .
the rescue mission was completed in the early morning of 21st .
according to the introduction by jixi mine group chairman yu jiahua , the mine , where the accident took place , was originally owned by the bankrupted muleng mine company and has an annual production of 200 thousand tons .
the gas explosion was not at the excavation layer but at the retreating alley .
at time of the accident , the workers were in the pits moving equipment .
the cause of the explosion is not known .
after the accident , jixi mine group promptly dispatched a rescue team with more than 40 members . apart from the 16 killed , the rest of the personnel were safely transferred .
the remains of the victims had been transported to the surface . body identification , as well as other work to deal with problems after the accident is currently in progress .
the ventilation system in the pit has already resumed normal operation .
after the accident , heilongjiang administration of coal mine safety and the related leaders of jixi had promptly arrived the scene to organize a rescue . the cause of the accident is under investigation .
bank of japan decided to maintain existing monetary policy
xinhua news agency , tokyo , january 22 ( reporter : yue shaoyan ) - the policy board of the bank of japan , the central bank in japan , decided in a meeting on the 22nd to maintain the existing monetary policy . the central bank will continue to provide the market with a total funding of 15,000 billion to 20,000 billion yen ( us $ 1 equals to 118 yen ) .
as to the government and the ruling party &apos;s request to &quot; adopt an appropriate inflation target &quot; , the meeting was of the opinion that one should adopt a cautious attitude about the issue .
the meeting believed that notwithstanding japan &apos;s economic prospect still looks gloom , the stock market and the financial markets have already stabilized . given there is no major change in the overall economy , the meeting decided to maintain the existing monetary policy .
regarding the government and the ruling party &apos;s request to further relax the bank &apos;s monetary policy as well as to establish an appropriate inflation target , the central bank believed that the financial markets in japan have an abundant supply of funds at this moment .
if the financial markets have a shortage of funds in the future , the central bank will inject more funds according to needs .
it is understood that the japanese government and the ruling party hopes the central bank can induce the price level inside japan to inflate at a rate of 1-3 percent a year .
a war on iraq may cause abundant supply in international oil market
xinhua news agency , riyadh , january 22 - saudi arabian newspaper al-watan quoted on 22nd the words of shakib khalil , algerian minister of energy and mines , who said the organization of the petroleum exporting countries ( opec ) cannot cover the daily shortage of 5 million barrels of crude oil in international markets in event of a war on iraq .
khalil said , among the members of opec , only saudi arabia and united arab emirates have the capacity to increase production .
&quot; opec has a problem in meeting with demands in the market because only saudi arabia and united arab emirates have spare capacity to increase production , but they can only produce 3 million barrels a day , &quot; he said .
since december last year , the price of crude oil in international markets keeps on surging due to the massive strike in venezuela and the threat of an iraq war .
opec decided on the 12th in vienna to increase the daily production of crude oil by 1.5 million barrels starting from february .
as u.s. and britain continue to dispatch soldiers to the gulf areas , the threat of an iraq war has not receded and hence , oil price in international markets continued to surge on the 21st .
khalil said the current oil price in international markets is affected more by tensions in international politics than actual demand and supply .
the customs department at shenzhen luohu is severely cracking down money smuggling
xinhua news agency , shenzhen , january 25 ( li nanling and li xiangzhi ) - the customs department at shenzhen luohu is severely cracking down any money smuggling through this tourist inspection channel , while preserving a civilized and highly efficient supervision .
last year , customs at luohu detected 1023 cases of money smuggling involving more than 150 million renminbi . among these cases , 15 cases had a single case value of more than 500 thousand renminbi ( excluding cases involving foreign currency money orders ) .
as china &apos;s biggest tourist inspection port , the luohu customs is given the job to supervise a tourist flow of 250 thousand person-times a day . if the rather common phenomenon of carrying more than the permitted amount of money is not tightly controlled , then there could be a considerable amount of currency drain every day .
facing a situation like this , the customs at luohu have finally adopted strict monitoring measures , including more frequent and more careful checks , in order to keep a sharp eye on possible money drain from china .
at about 9 : 00 a.m. on february 19 last year , a custom officer spotted a middle age woman who was pulling a suitcase and moving along in a very fast pace .
as the luggage case passed through the inspection machine , the custom officer noticed some suspicious object inside the suitcase . the officer requested the tourist to open the suitcase for inspection and was astonished to find three large bundles of hong kong dollars in thousand dollar bills inside a black plastic bag . the total value was 3 million hong kong dollars .
that was the most serious case of a tourist carrying cash items in excess of permitted limit at luohu customs in two years .
around july and august last year , offshore &quot; black market money changers &quot; attempted to smuggle a large quantity of foreign currency out of china . these changers wanted to take advantage of the massive tourists flow in summer holiday , as well as the renovation undergoing at the luohu port , which caused officers to work in a crowed environment .
the customs at luohu attached high importance to the issue and re-deployed manpower on a priority basis . the officers were determined to crack down any foreign currency smuggling activities by &quot; black market money changers &quot; .
during july 2 to august 11 , customs at luohu detected 4 cases of foreign currency smuggling by &quot; black market money changers &quot; , which had an equivalent value of 1.46 million renminbi .
tibet held gathering to celebrate spring festival and tibetan new year
xinhua news agency , lhasa , january 27 ( reporter : laba-ciren ) - more than 300 representatives from different trades , professions , ethnic races and circles in tibet attended the spring festival and tibetan new year gathering in the jiji multi-function room of lhasa hotel in the afternoon of the 27th . the event filled the whole multi-room with joy of the festival .
legqog , chairman of tibetan autonomous region , gave his new spring blessing to the people of all ethnic races in tibet ; all construction workers fighting bravely in the qinghai-tibet railway ; all members of the people &apos;s liberation army resident in tibet ; all armed police and public security officers ; as well as all overseas tibetans .
he said that in the past one year , the party committee and government of the autonomous region had led all ethnic races in tibet in a united way under the cordial care of the central committee and state department ; as well as the unselfish support from people of all races in china , especially those from province and cities designated to assist tibet and the key state-owned large enterprises . the party committee and the government of the autonomous region will hold on to the tibet guiding concept brought up at the beginning of the new century , which is to unite all people together and work hard ; develop and innovate ; maintain a continuous , rapid and healthy development in our national economy .
it is only then can tibet have the brilliant prospects of an efficient administration ; harmony among people ; a growth in the economy ; advances in the community ; unification among ethnic races ; stable state of affairs ; and people living merrily and in peace .
he pointed out that the new year is the first year for tibet to carry through and implement the spirit of the party &apos;s 16th national congress . this is also a critical year for tibet to push ahead its leap-over style of development and long-term political stability ; as well as laying the foundation for the development of a fairly prosperous and secure society .
tibet is to promote at all front a material civilization under socialism ; political civilization ; spiritual civilization and correctness ; coordination and development .
different units , including the song and dance ensemble of tibetan autonomous region , performed splendid shows during the gathering .
pagbalha geleg namgyai , vice chairman of the standing committee of the national people &apos;s congress also attended the gathering .
the association for the promotion of china &apos;s peaceful reunification in germany remembers the 8th anniversary of president jiang zemin &apos;s 8-point proposition on the taiwan issue
xinhua news agency , berlin , january 27 - in germany , the association of overseas chinese and ethnic chinese for the promotion of china &apos;s peaceful reunification issued a statement on 26th in memory of the 8th anniversary of chinese president jiang zemin &apos;s important speech - &quot; we should continue to promote and strive for the great undertaking of peaceful reunification of the motherland &quot; .
the statement reviewed the progress in relationship development between the two sides of the taiwan straits . it also looked at the cooperation between overseas compatriots from the two sides of the straits in &quot; opposing separation , opposing an independent taiwan and the promotion of a peaceful reunification of the motherland &quot; . the statement considered that the cooperation was adequate and effective .
the statement said president jiang zemin &apos;s important speech was a solid foundation to foster a beneficial and interactive cooperation between the chinese people on the sides of the strait as well as overseas compatriots . the speech insisted on the core principle of one china but it also encompassed the brothers and sisters affection between the chinese people on the two sides of the strait . the speech reflected the evolution of time and the vivid characteristic of an era . it dealt with the reality in a practical way , while retaining flexibility , toleration and consistency in the final solution of the problem .
according to the statement , president jiang zemin &apos;s 8-point proposition had comprehensively maintained and represented the fundamental interests of the chinese people on the two sides of the strait as well as overseas compatriots .
the statement urged overseas compatriots to make unceasing and new efforts to promote the reunification of the motherland .
the chinese culture festival inaugurated in ankara
xinhua news agency , ankara , january 28 ( reporter : zheng jinfa and huai chengbo ) - the &quot; chinese culture festival &quot; with the theme of &quot; chinese-turkish celebrate the spring festival together &quot; inaugurated on the evening of 28th at the grand hall of ankara trade center in ankara , capital of turkey .
the hebei provincial song and dance theatre of china performed splendid programs in dances and acrobatics , which deeply attracted over 1500 turkish viewers .
in this evening , many viewers had come to the grand hall very early in order to occupy the best seats .
the grand hall was completely full well before the performance began . many viewers were forced to stand in crowded positions at the corridor and a lot of children had to peep through interstices of heavy curtains in order to view the performance of chinese actors .
a dance featuring hebei locality , with the name of &quot; running a donkey &quot; , expressed an interesting episode about a young couple went back to the family of the wife &apos;s parents on a donkey .
the exquisite performance and the humorous plot impressed the turkish viewers . they exploded into laughter from time to time and clapped their hands enthusiastically .
when chinese singer / actor di fang sang out the famous turkish folk song &quot; great mountain &quot; in a clear voice , the whole hall applauded in thunderous clapping .
as soon as the performance was finished , many turkish viewers rushed to the stage and held out their hand or paper for autographs of chinese actors . some viewers even climbed onto the stage and took photos with the chinese actors . some turkish children had shed tears because they failed to obtain an autograph or could not take a joint photo with chinese actors .
a young turkish girl told xinhua news agency , &quot; it is the first time that i saw such beautiful chinese dances .
i hope that different kinds of troupes can come and perform in turkey such that we can understand the chinese culture better . &quot;
( hong kong , macau and taiwan ) mainland customers become major shoppers for hong kong &apos;s gold shops
xinhua news agency , hong kong , january 29 - according to koo tong fat , administration manager of hong kong &apos;s chow tai fook jewellery co . ltd . , mainland customers have become the main customer source for hong kong &apos;s gold and jewellery shops .
he said spending of mainland customers accounted for 30-40 percent of the total sales of gold shops in the last christmas and new year seasons . mainland customers are now one of the biggest consumer groups for hong kong &apos;s gold and jewellery industry .
tourists from mainland china have shown massive growth after the restriction to travel to hong kong was lifted at the beginning of 2002 .
during the chinese lunar new year , may 1 labor day , the golden week of october 1 , christmas and new year seasons , mainland china tourists are pushing forward hong kong &apos;s retail industry , especially in high-end consumer goods market .
the related departments in hong kong estimated that there would be about 600 thousand tourists from mainland china in the coming chinese lunar new year . many shops , especially the high-end shops , have focused on how to consolidate and develop the market of mainland china tourists .
chow tai fook jewellery expects the sales in the spring festival to grow by 5 percent .
in order to cope with the needs of mainland customers , some companies are starting to modify their operation and strategy . many companies have stepped up employee training in mandarin . companies are also launching new courses to improve employee &apos;s manner and service quality .
in general , many established gold and jewellery shops do not provide discounts . however , in order to attract more mainland customers , most of these established shops are now offering concessions if mainland china tourists pay in cash .
( international ) cambodian protesters set fire to thai embassy in cambodia
xinhua news agency , phnom penh , january 29 ( reporter : lei bosong and zhang ruiling ) - nearly one thousand cambodians broke into the thai embassy in cambodia on the 29th . they burned thai flags , cars and also set fire to the embassy building .
cambodian police is trying to contain the situation and several fire-fighting engines were dispatched .
the cambodian police cannot confirm whether there is any casualty at this moment .
protests took place in the morning of the day as an objection to the opinion by the thai actress suwanan kongying that the &quot; angkor wat temple belonged to thailand &quot; .
later in the day , more and more protesters gathered at the thai embassy in cambodia . they started to burn car tires , thai flags and portraits of that thai actress . the crowd then broke into the embassy .
according to another report , suwanan held a press conference in thailand and denied that she ever made any statement like the &quot; angkor wat temple belonged to thailand &quot; .
( international ) france dispatched gendarmes to reinforce peace keeping troops in ivory coast
xinhua news agency , paris , january 29 ( reporter : wang jingcheng ) - the french foreign minister , dominique de villepin , announced in a parliament hearing on the 29th that france had dispatched gendarmes to the republic of cote d &apos;ivoire ( ivory coast ) a few days ago . the reinforcement is to ensure the proper implementation of the peace agreement made by the different parties in ivory coast and also to strengthen the french peace keeping troops there .
de villepin did not specify the size of the reinforcement troop .
however , he said france had adopted all necessary measures to ensure the safety of french nationals in ivory coast .
he said france would be responsible to supervise the peace agreement in ivory coast under the support of international community . the authority of ivory coast government has to be restored and the completeness of its sovereignty has to be protected . france is going to contribute efforts to carry out the agreement alongside with the various parties to the agreement .
de villepin said the different parties in ivory coast have reached a peace agreement in paris on the 24th , which &quot; is a reliable guarantee to realize peace and national reconciliation in ivory coast &quot; .
in order to push ahead the implementation of the peace agreement , he will maintain close contacts with ivory coast president laurent gbagbo and leaders of other political parties .
he said air france &apos;s scheduled flights between abidjan and paris have resumed on 29th after a 3-day interruption .
( international ) protest held in nicaragua against war on iraq
xinhua news agency , managua , january 30 ( reporter : yang wenzheng ) - several hundred anti-war demonstrators held a protest outside the u.s. embassy in nicaragua on the 30th . they were strongly protesting the prospect of an u.s. military attack on iraq .
nicaragua peace promotion association organized the protest and its chairman jeanine guerreiro condemned u.s. for attempting to start a war to invade iraq and seize iraq &apos;s oil in a speech at the assembly .
protesters from managua , capital of nicaragua , and other cities were waiving signboards and shouting slogans like , &quot; we do not want any u.s. war on iraq ; we want world peace &quot; . they are demanding united states to stop all preparation activities for a war .
protesters said in a letter delivered to the u.s. embassy , &quot; let us fight together for world peace , freedom and a prosperous future . let us learn how to respect the rights of others . the iraq problem should be solved by iraq itself under the constructive assistance from international community . &quot;
( international ) poor growth in u.s. personal consumption expenditures in last year
xinhua news agency , washington , january 31 ( reporter : wang zhenhua ) - according to a report released by u.s. commerce department on the 31st , the growth in u.s. personal consumption expenditures in last year was at the same level as 2001 , which was a year of recession , notwithstanding a faster growth occurred in december last year .
u.s. personal consumption expenditures , the main power for economic growth , increased by 0.9 percent in december last year , and was the largest one month growth since july last year .
that growth included an increase of 6.1 percent in spending on durable goods and a small increase of 0.2 percent in spending on non-durable goods and services .
the numbers symbolized a less than robust spending in festival seasons in america .
personal consumption expenditures , which accounted for two-thirds of u.s. gross domestic products , showed a scant increase of 1 percent in the fourth quarter of last year . that growth was far lower than 4.2 percent in the third quarter and was the lowest quarterly growth since the first quarter of 1993 .
economic analysts believed that uncertain factors , including the looming u.s. war against iraq , sharp decline in stock market and a soft job market etc . , had inhibited the zeal to consume , which , in turn , becomes an important factor for a rapid slowdown in the u.s. economy in the fourth quarter .
for the whole year , u.s. personal consumption expenditures increased by 4.5 percent in last year , which was about the same growth as in 2001 .
the report also indicated that u.s. personal income increased by 0.4 percent in december last year .
for the whole year , u.s. personal income increased by 3 percent in last year , which was lower than the 3.3 percent growth in 2001 .
u.s. saving rate decreased from 4.5 percent in november to 4.1 percent in december because the growth rate in expenditure exceeded the growth rate in income .
( international ) the french army in ivory coast was attacked
xinhua news agency , abidjan , january 31 - local protesters attacked the french soldiers stationed in the republic of cote d &apos;ivoire ( ivory coast ) at the abidjan airport on the 31st . about 800 ivory coast youths threw stones at the french army and one french soldier was seriously injured at the face .
the chaos situation in ivory coast has escalated after the leaders of west african states held another meeting in the republic of senegal to deal with the civil war problem in ivory coast .
seydou diarra , a widely respected figure in the political circle , was nominated the new prime minister in the meeting . diarra had also returned to ivory coast on the 31st to build a coalition government .
however , the &quot; young patriots &quot; groups , supporter of ivory coast president laurent gbagbo , are dissatisfied that representatives of rebels are taking over important positions as defense and interior ministers in the future government .
they accused that the french government had forced gbagbo to accept the composition of the new government . they also claimed that diarra is a &quot; prime minister of the french people &quot; and threatened to kill him .
according to reports , the runway of abidjan airport had been cleared . however , several hundred members of the &quot; young patriots &quot; were still in the arrival hall and prepared to boycott diarra &apos;s return to ivory coast .
the civil war in ivory coast continued for 4 months and several hundred people were killed in the conflict .
on the 31st , french foreign affairs recommended the 16 thousand french nationals to evacuate the country as soon as possible .
( international ) a setback for the two canadian astronauts to join flights
xinhua news agency , ottawa , february 3 ( reporter : hu guangyao ) - according to reports of local media here on the 3rd , plans for two canadian astronauts to join flights on u.s. space shuttle in may and november this year received a setback due to the accident of the columbia space shuttle .
marc garneau , canadian space agency president and canada &apos;s first astronaut , said some scheduled missions for the international space station might be delayed pending u.s. investigation on the columbia accident . some plans might be carried out at a later date but some might be cancelled .
canadian astronauts steve maclean and dave williams were to join flights set for may and november this year , respectively .
the two astronauts are currently receiving training in houston , united states .
three canadian astronauts had participated in space mission on board the columbia space shuttle during the 90s of the twentieth century .
garneau also disclosed that among the scientific experiments carried on board the columbia in its last mission , there were two items sponsored by canada .
these researches included a study on the growth of protein crystals and one of the objectives is to find cure for breast cancer and prostate cancer .
another report said u.s. national aeronautics and space administration shortened an astronaut training activity in canada immediately after columbia &apos;s accident .
in last week , seven astronauts finished their training at valcartier military base near quebec city and had returned to united states .
( international ) u.s. construction spending rose significantly in december last year
xinhua news agency , washington , february 3 ( reporter : he ying ) - u.s. commerce department said in its report on the 3rd that u.s. construction spending in december last year rose 1.2 percent over november and amounted to us $ 858.3 billion at a seasonally adjusted annual rate .
the report said residential construction spending amounted to us $ 434.6 billion at a seasonally adjusted annual rate in december last year , up 2.9 percent over november .
analysts believed the low interest rate was an important factor for the strong growth in residential construction spending .
at present , u.s. federal reserve committee maintains short-term interest at 1.2 percent , which is the lowest level in 41 year .
however , u.s. commercial construction spending showed an opposite trend to that of residential construction . in december last year , u.s. commercial construction spending was us $ 158.6 billion at a seasonally adjusted annual rate , a decrease of 1.9 percent over november .
analysts believed enterprises were unwilling to increase investments in factories and other facilities because there were uncertain factors affecting the future prospect of the u.s. economy .
in addition , worries of terrorists &apos; attacks also weighted against commercial construction activities . president george w. bush signed the terrorism risk insurance act in november last year but the law cannot remove all concerns of investors and businesses .
judging from the performance of the whole year , the growth rate of u.s. residential construction spending decreased from 2.7 percent in 2001 to 0.4 percent , which was the lowest level since 1991 .
( international ) un inspectors found another empty chemical warhead in iraq
xinhua news agency , baghdad , february 4 ( reporter : wang bo and liang youchang ) - united nations ( un ) weapons inspection teams spokesman hiro ueki said in a press release on the 4th that inspectors found another empty chemical warhead on that day during an inspection at a suspicious location in iraq .
hiro ueki said inspectors found the empty chemical warhead at the al taji ammunition depot in the rural area north of baghdad in the course of an inspection .
the warhead was tagged and was kept in good condition .
he said the warhead was of the same type as the 12 empty chemical warheads found at another ammunition depot in southern iraq on january 16 .
shortly after inspectors found the aforesaid batch of empty chemical warheads , iraq said it found four more of such warheads at taji and had handed over the warheads to inspectors .
in the un monitoring , verification and inspection commission , executive chairman , hans blix &apos;s progress report to un security council on january 27 , blix said iraqi government should have declared these empty chemical warheads in its weapon report to un . inspectors are not supposed to look for them .
inspectors also called at 7 locations near baghdad on that day , which included a water purification station , an agricultural chemical factory , two missile factories and a weapon center originally built for development of chemical weapons .
inspectors also checked a sugar factory and a yeast factory on the 4th in mosul , a city in northern iraq .
shanghai police confirmed that the two men fell from air france jetliner were turkish nationals
xinhua news agency , shanghai , february 10 ( yang jinzhi and yang ye ) - shanghai police confirmed that the two men fell from air france flight af112 on january 23 were turkish nationals after a comparison of fingerprints . the two were 20-year old ramazan karacoban and 19-year old onur ozuyaman .
on january 23 at 10 : 58 a.m. , shanghai public security received a &quot; 110 &quot; emergency call , which said two men had fallen from the sky at the shengang village , laogang town of nanhui district . the two foreigners actually fell from a jetliner , which was about to land but was still flying from south towards the north direction .
after survey and investigation at the scene , shanghai police quickly determined that the dead men had fallen from the undercarriage area , which holds the landing gear , of an inbound air france flight af112 . air france also confirmed the conclusion .
after that , shanghai police had separately contacted the french and the turkish embassy in shanghai and cooperated with the police of the aforesaid two countries in the investigation .
based on the personal properties left behind by the two men at the scene , shanghai police made a guess about who they might be . a technical comparison was performed with the fingerprints and identities information supplied by turkish police . at the beginning of february , the police finally confirmed the identities of the two dead men after a match in fingerprints .
( hong kong , macau and taiwan ) macau achieved a fiscal surplus of 13 percent in last year
xinhua news agency , macau , february 10 ( reporter : li jie ) - according to information from macau special administrative region ( sar ) government , macau had carried out its 2002 fiscal budget in a successful manner . the surplus for the whole year was 1.7 billion patacas , which was equivalent to 13 percent of the fiscal budget for the year .
according to introduction , the 2002 fiscal budget for macau was a deficit budget at the time of compilation and it projected a deficit of 870 million patacas .
after netting off with the surplus in 2001 , macau should have a deficit of 300 million patacas . the plan was to finance the deficit from accumulated reserves .
however , the sar government tapped into new resources and economized on expenses during its specific implementation . as a result , actual income was 10 percent more than budget and actual expenditure was 8 percent lower than budget .
carlos avila , director of finance services bureau , said the successful removal of monopolies in gaming and telecommunications industries ; as well as the recovery in real estate and property market were the main reasons for above budget revenues in 2002 .
according to statistics , revenue from gaming taxes in 2002 rose substantially over 2001 . also , there was a massive growth of customers in the telecommunications industry . the real estate market was also active and revenue from stamp duty payable on property transfers had increased by 30 percent .
( hong kong , macau and taiwan ) macau passed legalization to avoid double tax
xinhua news agency , macau , february 11 - the legislative assembly of macau special administrative region ( sar ) passed a new law on 10th , which gives the sar chief executive the power to sign double tax treaties with other foreign regions .
&quot; double tax &quot; means two or more tax jurisdiction are taxing the same tax payer for the same or similar taxes at the same time on the same taxable event .
the idea of the law is that until such time a double tax treaty is signed between different regions , the sar chief executive has the power to adopt necessary measures to standardize the procedures , in event of a tax payer in macau is double taxed .
a member of the legislative assembly , who was responsible to scrutinize the law , &quot; taxation system in case of international or regional double taxation &quot; , said the trend of globalization is increasingly obvious . hence , taxation system must catch up otherwise the flow of capital , goods and human resources will be inhibited .
macau has to sign double tax treaties with other regions , which will help macau to attract more foreign capital as well as for macau to invest overseas . such a treaty is an important element for the promotion of economic development .
