last year , macau received 11.53 million tourists and mainland china tourists accounted for 4.24 million person-times . in the fourth quarter of the last year , the number of mainland china tourists had exceeded the number of hong kong tourists and became the number one customer source to macau .
these tourists stayed in macau for an average of 28.8 hours but the average spending per person was 2560 patacas , which was 64 percent higher than the average of all tourists .
analysis showed that jewellery / watches and garment / fabric are popular goods for tourists from all areas and the two categories accounted for 27 percent and 23 percent of their spending in macau .
