the shenyang city of liaoning province is an economic hub for northeast china .
according to introduction by wang xiangkun , deputy major of shenyang city , hunnan new district is to be developed into an important base for it industries in northern china . more and more it enterprises have already selected to settle down in hunnan .
( international ) china and chile signed a memorandum of understanding in sanitary and phytosanitary measures
xinhua news agency , santiago , february 17 ( reporter : hou yaoqi ) - general administration of quality supervision , inspection and quarantine of china ( aqsiq ) has signed a memorandum of understanding ( mou ) in &quot; sanitary and phytosanitary measures &quot; with chile &apos;s agricultural department on the 17th here in chile .
