the mou stipulated that the two sides are to strictly adhere to any agreed protocol or any decided inspection and quarantine requirements . the two sides are to implement the requirements into specific inspection and quarantine procedures applicable to animals , plants , animal / plant products and related foodstuffs entering or leaving the countries . the two sides will step up the efforts to solve any market access problems for animals , plants , animal / plant products and related foodstuffs through scientific basis .
