( international ) blix demands iraq to start the destruction of al-samoud missiles within one week
xinhua news agency , united nations , february 22 - according to media reports here on the 22nd , hans blix , executive chairman of united nations monitoring , verification and inspection commission ( unmovic ) has already issued an ultimatum to iraq demanding the country to begin the destruction of al-samoud missiles within one week .
